title: Cabinet to discuss new powers to tackle anti-social behaviour (Northampton Borough Council)
text: ( Source : Northampton Borough Council ) Northampton Borough Council's Cabinet will meet next week to discuss proposals for new powers to address anti-social behaviour in Northampton 's public places. Public Space Protection Orders (PSPOs)
